Jenkins in an open source automation server that supports building, deploying and automating any project.

[https://github.com/rmuslimov/jenkins.el jenkins.el] is a Jenkins UI in emacs

[https://github.com/AshtonKem/Butler Butler] - another Jenkins/Hudson UI in Emacs.

[https://github.com/ataylor284/jenkins-watch jenkins-watch] Display jenkins/hudson build status on the emacs modeline

[https://github.com/john2x/jenkinsfile-mode jenkinsfile-mode] is available for editing a <code>Jenkinsfile</code>. It requires <code>groovy-mode</code>. It is available from MELPA.

Also see [[CircleCI]] and [[Travis]].
